name: Kra-ZLogic
body: Kra-ZLogic is a 64 bit logic calculator used to compute simple whole number equations. Kra-Z Logic also supports converting to and from Binary, Octal, Decimal, and Hexadecimal
tagline: Kra-ZLogic - 64 bit Programmers Calculator for iOS.
